      <title>2025 年，政治而非气候将推动可持续金融趋势</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/politics-not-climate-drive-sustainable-finance-trends-2025-2025-01-10/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[2025年对于可持续金融来说仍将是动荡的一年，因为唐纳德·特朗普再次出任美国总统预示着从资金流动到法律案件和市场监管等各个方面地区分歧将进一步加剧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/politics-not-climate-drive-sustainable-finance-trends-2025-2025-01-10/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 10:32:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>联合信贷银行将证券托管服务引入内部，重点关注德国</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/unicredit-brings-security-custody-services-in-house-with-focus-germany-2025-01-10/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利联合信贷银行周五表示，将引入内部安全托管服务，最初重点关注德国，此举将在那里创造 140 个新的工作岗位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/unicredit-brings-security-custody-services-in-house-with-focus-germany-2025-01-10/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 10:06:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国央行正加速接近政策底线</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-central-bank-is-moving-faster-towards-its-policy-limits-2025-01-10/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国人民银行宣布因资产稀缺性而暂停购买国债，凸显出其在面临日益严峻的经济环境时的资源局限性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-central-bank-is-moving-faster-towards-its-policy-limits-2025-01-10/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 07:24:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
