      <title>野村证券聘请 Sudhir Nemali 担任国际财富首席运营官</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/nomura-hires-sudhir-nemali-international-wealth-chief-operating-officer-2025-01-10/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据路透社周五看到的一份内部备忘录显示，日本野村控股已任命苏迪尔·内马利（Sudhir Nemali）为其国际财富管理业务的董事总经理兼首席运营官。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/nomura-hires-sudhir-nemali-international-wealth-chief-operating-officer-2025-01-10/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 03:33:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>融创清算诉讼重创股价 再度引发房地产债务危机担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/sunac-china-shares-plunge-after-liquidation-petition-filed-against-developer-2025-01-10/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五，在开发商融创中国被提起清算申请后，该公司股价和债券大幅下跌，尽管中国政府采取了复苏措施，但再次引发了投资者对房地产行业债务危机的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/sunac-china-shares-plunge-after-liquidation-petition-filed-against-developer-2025-01-10/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 02:39:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>消息人士称，美国银行投资银行家的奖金将增加约 10%</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/bank-america-bonuses-investment-bankers-rise-about-10-source-says-2025-01-09/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位知情人士向路透社透露，美国银行投资银行家的奖金池可能比去年增加 10%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/bank-america-bonuses-investment-bankers-rise-about-10-source-says-2025-01-09/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 22:39:04 GMT</pubDate>
